summary:
Experienced product manager with >7y of international experience across market leaders in travel, retail and search verticals, both in permanent and consulting capacity, across platforms incl. native apps and B2B as well as B2C domains.

 ~ Happiest when solving real business problems with pragmatic and customer-centric solutions, from conceptualisation to execution.

~ Specialising in new product development but equally at home in optimisation of scaled up products. 

~ Comfortable with application of machine learning solutions where relevant to the problem at hand.

~ Experienced in people management with a strong track record in methodical approach to
people growth.
